#' @return an instance of \code{DnaSeq} or \code{RnaSeq}.
#' @seealso \code{\linkS4class{GenericSeq}}, \code{\linkS4class{DnaSeq}} and \code{\linkS4class{RnaSeq}}.
#' @examples
